  2 |  * Iteration Governor - Safety mechanism for preventing runaway agent loops
  3 |  * 
  4 |  * Features:
  5 |  * - Track iteration counts per agent/task
  6 |  * - Configurable max iteration limits (default: 10 for simple tasks, 50 for complex)
  7 |  * - Per-agent limits support (different agents can have different limits)
  8 |  * - Circuit breaker pattern - if errors exceed threshold, pause the agent
  9 |  * - Warning logs when approaching limits
